## ğŸ› ï¸ Available Endpoints

### **Users**
| Method | Endpoint      | Description       |
|--------|-------------|------------------|
| `POST` | `/users/`   | Create User      |
| `GET`  | `/users/`   | Get All Users    |
| `PUT`  | `/users/{id}` | Update User    |

### **Purchases**
| Method | Endpoint      | Description       |
|--------|-------------|------------------|
| `POST` | `/purchases/`   | Create Purchase  |
| `GET`  | `/purchases/`   | Get All Purchases  |

